ðŸ“Œ Project Overview
Face detection is one of the fundamental applications of computer vision. In this project, we use OpenCV's CascadeClassifier and a pre-trained model (haarcascade_frontalface_alt.xml) to detect faces from a live webcam stream. This can be extended to face recognition, attendance systems, surveillance bots, and more.

ðŸ”§ Technologies Used
Tool/Library	              Purpose
Python 3.x	         Core programming language.
OpenCV	             Real-time computer vision library used for video capturing and face detection.
Haar Cascade XML	   Pre-trained model used to detect facial features.

